This is a tutorial on how to get katoolin on ubuntu linux.


#alexanderclamshell~: sudo su


(enter password for alexanderclamshell)


#rootalexanderclamshell~: katoolin


This will load a screen saying katoolin. The numbers will symbolize what you type in.


The first number you want to type is the number next to the word update


once it is done, you have to exit and open it again. 


Then choose the number next to the words view categories


It will show a list of the types of hacks you can get.


When you know what you want to download, just press the number and it will automatically download.


Then to open it just put the root option back on your terminal, then type in the words that described the type of hack you downloaded, good luck.
